&lt;b&gt;of those three options that&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:19.583 --> 00:00:20.750
&lt;b&gt;they put on the table&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:20.791 --> 00:00:23.750
&lt;b&gt;would be adopted, but fortunately&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:25.000
&lt;b&gt;we avoided&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.416
&lt;b&gt;a serious cause of war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:28.708 --> 00:00:31.000
&lt;b&gt;So, when someone steals 200&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.500
&lt;b&gt;billion euros from you,&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:33.708
&lt;b&gt;freezing is one thing.&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:33.708 --> 00:00:37.083
&lt;b&gt;That has been seen. So, in history&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:37.083 --> 00:00:39.541
&lt;b&gt;more modern, and earlier around the second&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:39.541 --> 00:00:40.750
&lt;b&gt;world war etc.&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.708
&lt;b&gt;So, we've already seen that. But&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:42.708 --> 00:00:45.333
&lt;b&gt;we haven't seen money theft yet.&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:45.541 --> 00:00:48.541
&lt;b&gt;And stealing 200 billion euros is&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:48.541 --> 00:00:50.208
&lt;b&gt;definitely and certainly&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:50.208 --> 00:00:51.875
&lt;b&gt;a good reason for war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:52.208 --> 00:00:55.291
&lt;b&gt;Why is someone pushing so hard and why&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:55.291 --> 00:00:57.750
&lt;b&gt;that part of the leaders of the EU member states&lt;/b&gt;

00:00:57.750 --> 00:01:01.875
&lt;b&gt;wants to fight with Russia so much and&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:01.875 --> 00:01:03.500
&lt;b&gt;wants millions&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.041
&lt;b&gt;of people to lose their lives,&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:05.166 --> 00:01:07.083
&lt;b&gt;I just can't wrap my head around it.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:07.083 --> 00:01:08.916
&lt;b&gt;And it's even harder for me to&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:08.916 --> 00:01:10.583
&lt;b&gt;understand how it is possible&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:10.583 --> 00:01:13.875
&lt;b&gt;that so many EU citizens want to&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:13.875 --> 00:01:15.333
&lt;b&gt;lose their lives and&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:15.333 --> 00:01:16.791
&lt;b&gt;want to fight, etc.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:17.416 --> 00:01:20.375
&lt;b&gt;War is a terrible situation in&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:20.375 --> 00:01:21.750
&lt;b&gt;the life of every man,&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:21.958 --> 00:01:23.666
&lt;b&gt;who has even the slightest contact with&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:23.666 --> 00:01:26.166
&lt;b&gt;war. So, it's something terrible.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:26.458 --> 00:01:30.666
&lt;b&gt;And that so many EU citizens want to&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:30.666 --> 00:01:32.083
&lt;b&gt;fight, it is&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:32.083 --> 00:01:33.291
&lt;b&gt;really unbelievable to me.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:33.583 --> 00:01:35.250
&lt;b&gt;But well, the least evil happened&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:37.875
&lt;b&gt;as far as the war is concerned.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:38.541 --> 00:01:40.708
&lt;b&gt;And the greatest evil in terms of&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:40.708 --> 00:01:42.708
&lt;b&gt;economic future&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:42.708 --> 00:01:44.791
&lt;b&gt;of every EU citizen.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:44.791 --> 00:01:47.500
&lt;b&gt;Of course, it will affect&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:49.333
&lt;b&gt;poor&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:49.333 --> 00:01:51.125
&lt;b&gt;countries like Croatia much more,&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:51.375 --> 00:01:55.375
&lt;b&gt;and somewhat less countries that are, let's&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:55.375 --> 00:01:57.625
&lt;b&gt;say, much more economically developed.&lt;/b&gt;

00:01:58.250 --> 00:02:00.708
&lt;b&gt;Well, what happened? It happened&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:00.708 --> 00:02:03.875
&lt;b&gt;that the EU leaders&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:03.875 --> 00:02:08.041
&lt;b&gt;indebted 24 EU countries,&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:11.291
&lt;b&gt;except Slovakia, Hungary and the Czech Republic,&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:11.291 --> 00:02:12.625
&lt;b&gt;at least that's what they say,&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:13.125 --> 00:02:17.166
&lt;b&gt;for the amount of 90 billion euros that they&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:17.166 --> 00:02:18.541
&lt;b&gt;want to send irrevocably&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:18.541 --> 00:02:20.041
&lt;b&gt;to Ukraine.&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:21.375 --> 00:02:23.500
&lt;b&gt;Now, they say, they say&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:23.500 --> 00:02:25.541
&lt;b&gt;loan, but who is raising that loan?&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:25.541 --> 00:02:26.000
&lt;b&gt;Is Ukraine raising it?&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.500
&lt;b&gt;Of course not.&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:27.916 --> 00:02:31.833
&lt;b&gt;EU citizens are raising it. So we are&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:31.833 --> 00:02:32.708
&lt;b&gt;raising it and we will&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:32.708 --> 00:02:33.708
&lt;b&gt;have to pay it back.&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:34.125 --> 00:02:35.541
&lt;b&gt;No one else will pay it back. Well,&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:35.541 --> 00:02:37.166
&lt;b&gt;where would Ukraine pay it back from?&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:37.416 --> 00:02:41.125
&lt;b&gt;They say Russia will pay it back, because&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:41.125 --> 00:02:42.250
&lt;b&gt;it will be responsible for&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:42.250 --> 00:02:44.000
&lt;b&gt;paying war damages to Ukraine,&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:44.375 --> 00:02:45.291
&lt;b&gt;so Ukraine will from&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:45.291 --> 00:02:46.500
&lt;b&gt;that money. Well, like this.&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:46.916 --> 00:02:49.000
&lt;b&gt;So, let's go back a little to the&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.375
&lt;b&gt;basics of law, to&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:50.375 --> 00:02:52.333
&lt;b&gt;the basic foundations of law.&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:52.583 --> 00:02:55.625
&lt;b&gt;In order for compensation&lt;/b&gt;

00:02:55.625 --> 00:02:59.166
&lt;b&gt;for damages to exist, there must also be a war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:00.291 --> 00:03:02.791
&lt;b&gt;forced all the time that the pledge&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:02.791 --> 00:03:04.791
&lt;b&gt;theoretically impossible that&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:04.791 --> 00:03:06.375
&lt;b&gt;in any procedure&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:06.791 --> 00:03:10.875
&lt;b&gt;there is war damage. So, without&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:10.875 --> 00:03:13.291
&lt;b&gt;a declaration of war, there is no war damage.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:13.625 --> 00:03:15.750
&lt;b&gt;Now, how is that possible? That&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:15.750 --> 00:03:17.041
&lt;b&gt;we still don't have a war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:17.833 --> 00:03:20.583
&lt;b&gt;So, the war can be offensive or&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:20.583 --> 00:03:22.000
&lt;b&gt;it can be defensive.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:22.500 --> 00:03:23.500
&lt;b&gt;What is needed&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:23.500 --> 00:03:25.000
&lt;b&gt;for a war to even arise?&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:25.250 --> 00:03:26.458
&lt;b&gt;So, an armed conflict is not&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:26.458 --> 00:03:28.000
&lt;b&gt;enough for war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:30.750
&lt;b&gt;We see countless armed conflicts&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:30.750 --> 00:03:32.958
&lt;b&gt;every day around the world.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:33.375 --> 00:03:34.416
&lt;b&gt;So, America&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:34.416 --> 00:03:36.791
&lt;b&gt;bombed Syria now.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:36.791 --> 00:03:38.583
&lt;b&gt;Is it at war with Syria? No.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:39.125 --> 00:03:41.083
&lt;b&gt;Before that, it bombed Iran.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:41.083 --> 00:03:43.208
&lt;b&gt;Is it at war with Iran? No.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:43.458 --> 00:03:46.041
&lt;b&gt;Because armed conflicts are not war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:46.541 --> 00:03:50.583
&lt;b&gt;War has its own legal definition.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:50.833 --> 00:03:54.166
&lt;b&gt;War must be declared by the legitimate&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:54.166 --> 00:03:55.791
&lt;b&gt;government of a certain country.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:56.416 --> 00:03:57.208
&lt;b&gt;So, Russia&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:57.208 --> 00:03:58.750
&lt;b&gt;says, we are not at war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:58.750 --> 00:03:59.500
&lt;b&gt;We are conducting&lt;/b&gt;

00:03:59.500 --> 00:04:02.375
&lt;b&gt;a special military action.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:02.500 --> 00:04:04.208
&lt;b&gt;A special military operation.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:04.416 --> 00:04:06.833
&lt;b&gt;As Putin likes to say.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:06.833 --> 00:04:09.166
&lt;b&gt;And Ukraine, the Ukrainian Parliament,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:09.958 --> 00:04:10.666
&lt;b&gt;never&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:10.666 --> 00:04:12.083
&lt;b&gt;declared a defensive war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:12.541 --> 00:04:15.625
&lt;b&gt;So, compensation for damages in any&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:15.625 --> 00:04:17.541
&lt;b&gt;legitimate procedure,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:17.750 --> 00:04:19.791
&lt;b&gt;cannot occur because there is no war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:20.208 --> 00:04:21.416
&lt;b&gt;So, Russia and&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:21.416 --> 00:04:24.416
&lt;b&gt;Ukraine are not formally at war,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:24.833 --> 00:04:27.458
&lt;b&gt;because neither party&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:27.458 --> 00:04:28.625
&lt;b&gt;in the conflict has declared it.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:29.250 --> 00:04:30.833
&lt;b&gt;So, let's formally&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:30.833 --> 00:04:32.500
&lt;b&gt;legally forget&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:32.500 --> 00:04:36.208
&lt;b&gt;the situation that can never actually&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:36.208 --> 00:04:37.666
&lt;b&gt;happen,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:38.250 --> 00:04:40.916
&lt;b&gt;and that is that Russia would in any&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:40.916 --> 00:04:43.458
&lt;b&gt;variant pay war damages.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:43.833 --> 00:04:45.291
&lt;b&gt;So, Russia would have to be&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:45.291 --> 00:04:47.333
&lt;b&gt;completely defeated and crushed,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:47.750 --> 00:04:48.875
&lt;b&gt;and if it is completely&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:48.875 --> 00:04:50.041
&lt;b&gt;defeated and crushed,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:50.041 --> 00:04:51.333
&lt;b&gt;then there is nowhere to pay from.&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:51.708 --> 00:04:53.541
&lt;b&gt;But in order for Russia to be completely&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:53.541 --> 00:04:54.791
&lt;b&gt;crushed and defeated,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:55.250 --> 00:04:58.625
&lt;b&gt;Europe would certainly not exist,&lt;/b&gt;

00:04:58.833 --> 00:05:01.041
&lt;b&gt;because it would disappear in a nuclear war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:01.208 --> 00:05:03.000
&lt;b&gt;Therefore, these are not realities.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:06.000
&lt;b&gt;That money will go irrevocably,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:06.208 --> 00:05:09.291
&lt;b&gt;90 billion euros will go irrevocably&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:09.291 --> 00:05:10.625
&lt;b&gt;to Ukraine,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:10.625 --> 00:05:13.416
&lt;b&gt;and that will be paid by EU citizens.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:15.083 --> 00:05:17.958
&lt;b&gt;EU citizens, many think that&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:17.958 --> 00:05:20.458
&lt;b&gt;the situation is great in the EU,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:20.916 --> 00:05:22.041
&lt;b&gt;that there is money to&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:22.041 --> 00:05:23.250
&lt;b&gt;throw around etc.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:23.875 --> 00:05:26.333
&lt;b&gt;The EU is already heavily indebted.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:26.333 --> 00:05:27.416
&lt;b&gt;It's not that there is no money,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:27.416 --> 00:05:28.916
&lt;b&gt;but it is heavily indebted&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:28.916 --> 00:05:30.500
&lt;b&gt;and cannot return&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:30.500 --> 00:05:31.583
&lt;b&gt;even current debts.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:32.208 --> 00:05:34.000
&lt;b&gt;As I have said countless times,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:34.333 --> 00:05:35.583
&lt;b&gt;Macron himself pointed out,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:35.958 --> 00:05:37.000
&lt;b&gt;because we were not&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.000
&lt;b&gt;able to pay&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:39.166
&lt;b&gt;even the first installment of&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:39.166 --> 00:05:41.208
&lt;b&gt;these 800 billion euros,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:41.208 --> 00:05:43.250
&lt;b&gt;which amounts to 30 billion.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:43.458 --> 00:05:44.291
&lt;b&gt;And why didn't we?&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:44.291 --> 00:05:46.166
&lt;b&gt;Because the total EU budget&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:46.625 --> 00:05:49.583
&lt;b&gt;is 200 billion,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:50.291 --> 00:05:52.791
&lt;b&gt;150 billion goes to payments,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:52.791 --> 00:05:55.375
&lt;b&gt;which means there isn't even a cent there,&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:55.833 --> 00:05:57.250
&lt;b&gt;not a cent for any&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:57.250 --> 00:05:58.916
&lt;b&gt;new borrowing.&lt;/b&gt;

00:05:58.916 --> 00:06:00.833
&lt;b&gt;And we see in the future,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:01.125 --> 00:06:02.541
&lt;b&gt;so we now have a future&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:02.541 --> 00:06:04.916
&lt;b&gt;seven-year period,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:05.125 --> 00:06:06.583
&lt;b&gt;in which the budget,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:06.583 --> 00:06:07.625
&lt;b&gt;so the seven-year budget&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:07.625 --> 00:06:08.833
&lt;b&gt;is 2000 billion,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:09.083 --> 00:06:10.625
&lt;b&gt;and the annual budgets&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:10.625 --> 00:06:12.500
&lt;b&gt;will amount to&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:12.500 --> 00:06:14.458
&lt;b&gt;300 billion euros each year.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:14.750 --> 00:06:16.750
&lt;b&gt;So, 30% more&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:19.041
&lt;b&gt;than the budget for 25.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:19.041 --> 00:06:22.708
&lt;b&gt;or 100% more than&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:22.708 --> 00:06:24.458
&lt;b&gt;the budget for 2016.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:26.041 --> 00:06:28.208
&lt;b&gt;Where does the money come from in the EU budget?&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:28.458 --> 00:06:29.458
&lt;b&gt;Exclusively from citizens.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:30.541 --> 00:06:31.875
&lt;b&gt;So only from citizens,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:31.875 --> 00:06:32.958
&lt;b&gt;it comes from&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:32.958 --> 00:06:35.083
&lt;b&gt;the budget of each country.&lt;/b&gt;

