&lt;b&gt;So, and the budget&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:36.208 --> 00:06:37.500
&lt;b&gt;is filled exclusively,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:37.833 --> 00:06:39.583
&lt;b&gt;it is filled by citizens from each country.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:40.083 --> 00:06:43.541
&lt;b&gt;So, that money, those 90 billion,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:43.541 --> 00:06:45.583
&lt;b&gt;will be paid by&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:45.583 --> 00:06:47.458
&lt;b&gt;EU citizens,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:47.458 --> 00:06:50.250
&lt;b&gt;but what are the citizens paying it for?&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:51.375 --> 00:06:52.458
&lt;b&gt;For the continuation of the war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:54.083 --> 00:06:55.708
&lt;b&gt;For the continuation of the war.&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:55.958 --> 00:06:58.041
&lt;b&gt;That money is not enough,&lt;/b&gt;

00:06:58.291 --> 00:06:59.083
&lt;b&gt;because Ukraine&lt;/b&gt;

