&lt;b&gt;not that Ukraine would be&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:08.291 --> 00:07:10.166
&lt;b&gt;several times more powerful,&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:10.375 --> 00:07:12.083
&lt;b&gt;but that the balance of power on the ground&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:12.083 --> 00:07:13.000
&lt;b&gt;would be exactly the same&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:15.708
&lt;b&gt;as it is today, so that's&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:15.708 --> 00:07:18.500
&lt;b&gt;66 billion euros per year.&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:18.833 --> 00:07:21.458
&lt;b&gt;So, from next year we will&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:21.458 --> 00:07:23.416
&lt;b&gt;have to send 90 billion&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:23.416 --> 00:07:25.958
&lt;b&gt;and so on ad infinitum.&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:25.958 --> 00:07:27.083
&lt;b&gt;That's how the&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:27.083 --> 00:07:29.333
&lt;b&gt;leaders of the EU member states imagined it.&lt;/b&gt;

00:07:30.166 --> 00:07:31.708
